article.description: — Quincy Olivari had 29 points in Xavier's 74-54 victory over Seton Hall on Saturday.
article.headline: Xavier secures 74-54 win over Seton Hall
article.linkText: Xavier secures 74-54 win over Seton Hall
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Quincy Olivari had 29 points in Xavier's 74-54 victory over Seton Hall on Saturday. Olivari added seven rebounds for the Musketeers (7-6, 1-1 Big East). Abou Ousmane scored 16 points and added 10 rebounds, three steals, and five blocks. Dayvion McKnight had 15 points and shot 6 for 15, including 3 for 5 from beyond the arc. Dre Davis led the Pirates (8-5, 1-1) in scoring, finishing with 18 points and two blocks. Seton Hall also got 13 points, eight rebounds and four steals from Kadary Richmond. Dylan Addae-Wusu also had six points and eight rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
